<lb n="3" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">kṣmāpatirddatvāna</hi><note n="425-1">Read <hi rend="grantha">tvānandam</hi></note> <hi rend="grantha">ntanidhim dvijan dhanadayannāmōdaya mmādhavam <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> puṇyē<unclear>lṛ</unclear>ghaiḥ paripālitasya paritō bhūtāḷisamv<unclear>ē</unclear>ṣṭitāssadvargaiśśabaḷikṛtasya satatākrāntā bhujaṅgaprajaiḥ prāptasyātinava praśastimadhika prakhyāta śauryyācyutakṣmāpānanta</hi><note n="425-1">Read <hi rend="grantha">tvānandam</hi></note> <hi rend="grantha">nidhērṇavāpi nidhayaḥ kintē labhantē tulām <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śubhamastu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi>
